  "url": "https://www.tamilmirror.lk/\u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd/\u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf-\u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd-\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1-\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd-\u0b87\u0bb0\u0b95\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf-\u0b85\u0bb1\u0bc8/175-300105",
  "time_ut": 1657422112,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd, \u0b87\u0bb0\u0b95\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b85\u0bb1\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Inside the bunker in the presidential palace, the secret room",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "While the Presidential Palace is fully under the control of the protesters, a bunker has been discovered there.",
        "In this case, it has now been revealed that there is a secret room inside that bunker.",
        "It is reported that this bunker is located in a special building in the Presidential Palace and can be accessed through different cupboard doors.",
        "It is also said that there is a very secret room at the bottom of this bunker and this secret room cannot be opened by very strong iron doors.",
        "However, the door of that room could not be opened so far and the protesters suspected that there might be some important features or things in it.",
        "However, the secret room is set up as a very air-conditioned room. It is reported that it can be felt through the cold air coming through the small gap at the bottom of the iron door of the room. (a)"
      ],
